<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1948-11-04T16:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1948-11-04T16:00:00-05:00" n="435" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d435">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">811.20200(D)/10–2748: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                    State</gloss> to the Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Stuart</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1948-11-04T16:00:00-05:00">November
                                    4, 1948—4 p. m.</date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>1545. Carefully considering urtel 2015 Oct. 27. Attempting increase
                            immediately present output materials needed expose threat international
                            communism to China. Pending full reply following soon, continue regular
                            program.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Lovett</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                </body></text></TEI>